synopsis.value: We travel through the strange landscape of the Astral Plane and eventually come across a small Gith military outpost. Here we find Kith'rak Voss. He’s exhausted and weak, but a malevolent triumph still sparkles in his eyes: we’re too late. He already sent the outpost’s scouts ahead. It’s only a matter of time before word reaches Vlaakith. Now he will fulfill his duty and kill us.
